fr.anthonyrey.connector

Class GlpiConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.anthonyrey.connector.GlpiConnector

  • public class GlpiConnector
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows you to connect to GLPI and the webservice It has everything to get tickets, close them and to log yourself into GLPI
    Author:
    anthonyrey
